@ClubSystem_HostAddress = http://localhost:5168

### Variables - Thay đổi các giá trị này
@student_token = YOUR_STUDENT_TOKEN_HERE
@clubleader_token = YOUR_CLUBLEADER_TOKEN_HERE
@membership_request_id = 1
@payment_id = 1
@club_id = 1
@account_id = 1
@activity_id = 1

###
### ============================================
### VNPAY PAYMENT TEST FLOW
### ============================================

### 1. Student: Gửi Membership Request
POST {{ClubSystem_HostAddress}}/api/student/membership/request
Authorization: Bearer {{student_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clubId": {{club_id}},
  "reason": "Tôi muốn tham gia CLB để học hỏi và phát triển kỹ năng"
}

### 2. Club Leader: Approve Membership Request
POST {{ClubSystem_HostAddress}}/api/leader/membership/{{membership_request_id}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{clubleader_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "note": "Chấp nhận yêu cầu"
}

### 3. Student: Tạo VNPay Payment URL
POST {{ClubSystem_HostAddress}}/api/payment/vnpay/create
Authorization: Bearer {{student_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "membershipRequestId": {{membership_request_id}}
}

### 4. Student: Kiểm tra Payment Status (tất cả CLB)
GET {{ClubSystem_HostAddress}}/api/payment/status
Authorization: Bearer {{student_token}}

### 5. Student: Xem Payment History
GET {{ClubSystem_HostAddress}}/api/payment/history
Authorization: Bearer {{student_token}}

### 6. VNPay ReturnUrl Callback (sau khi thanh toán)
# VNPay sẽ tự động gọi endpoint này với query parameters
# GET {{ClubSystem_HostAddress}}/api/payment/vnpay-return?vnp_Amount=...&vnp_ResponseCode=00&...

### 7. VNPay IPN Callback (xác nhận thanh toán)
# VNPay sẽ tự động gọi endpoint này
# POST {{ClubSystem_HostAddress}}/api/payment/vnpay-ipn

###
### ============================================
### STUDENT ACTIVITY TEST
### ============================================

### 1. Student: Xem Activities có thể đăng ký
GET {{ClubSystem_HostAddress}}/api/student/activities/available
Authorization: Bearer {{student_token}}

### 2. Student: Đăng ký tham gia Activity
POST {{ClubSystem_HostAddress}}/api/student/activities/{{activity_id}}/register
Authorization: Bearer {{student_token}}

### 3. Student: Xem lịch sử tham gia Activities
GET {{ClubSystem_HostAddress}}/api/student/activities/history
Authorization: Bearer {{student_token}}

### 4. Student: Hủy đăng ký Activity
DELETE {{ClubSystem_HostAddress}}/api/student/activities/{{activity_id}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{student_token}}

###
### ============================================
### CLUB LEADER PAYMENT MANAGEMENT
### ============================================

### 1. Club Leader: Xem tất cả payments của CLB
GET {{ClubSystem_HostAddress}}/api/leader/payment/club/{{club_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{clubleader_token}}

### 2. Club Leader: Xem payment history của một member
GET {{ClubSystem_HostAddress}}/api/leader/payment/club/{{club_id}}/member/{{account_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{clubleader_token}}

### 3. Club Leader: Xem danh sách members còn nợ phí
GET {{ClubSystem_HostAddress}}/api/leader/payment/club/{{club_id}}/debt
Authorization: Bearer {{clubleader_token}}

###
### ============================================
### OTHER ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Student: Xem thông tin account (để pre-fill form)
GET {{ClubSystem_HostAddress}}/api/student/membership/account-info
Authorization: Bearer {{student_token}}

### Student: Xem các membership requests của mình
GET {{ClubSystem_HostAddress}}/api/student/membership/requests
Authorization: Bearer {{student_token}}

